01:46.875 --> 01:49.125
DID YOU KNOW
GINSBERG REVIVED A PATIENT

01:49.166 --> 01:51.834
WHO WAS COMATOSE FOR 17 YEARS?
I'LL GET MY MIRACLE.

01:51.875 --> 01:55.125
