OH. HELLO.

02:22.959 --> 02:25.458
DR. MONTGOMERY OR DR. KING?
DR. MONTGOMERY.
PLEASURE TO MEET YOU.

02:25.500 --> 02:28.041
AND THIS IS EDDIE LINDY,
KAYLA'S HUSBAND.

02:28.083 --> 02:31.041
