02:37.250 --> 02:40.709
OKAY, UH, PATIENT IS
KAYLA LINDY, 32 YEARS OF AGE,

02:40.750 --> 02:43.041
SURROGATE MOTHER
PREGNANT WITH TRIPLETS.

02:43.083 --> 02:44.583
DURING THE PREGNANCY,

02:44.625 --> 02:46.083
