INTO NEUROSURGERY?

03:55.458 --> 03:57.875
IS THAT
THE GERALDINE GINSBERG?

03:57.917 --> 03:59.917
MY GOD.

03:59.959 --> 04:02.625
SAM BENNETT.
YOU STAYED HOT.

04:02.667 --> 04:04.041
