04:07.083 --> 04:09.667
WHAT HAPPENED?
NOW SHE IS
A FANCY NEUROSURGEON.

04:09.709 --> 04:13.417
OH! THERE YOU ARE.
TAKE YOUR KID.
OH.

04:13.458 --> 04:15.458
