OH, NO, NO, NO.
HE'S--HE'S NOT MINE.

04:25.917 --> 04:28.083
HE'S, UH,
HE'S MY BOYFRIEND'S SON.

04:28.125 --> 04:29.542
DR. SHEPHERD.

04:29.583 --> 04:31.750
