TALKING ABOUT? HUH?
(laughs)

04:50.166 --> 04:53.125
YEAH, THAT'S SAM.
THAT'S SAM. I THINK YOU ARE.
YOU'RE SO GOOD WITH HIM.

04:53.166 --> 04:56.125
