GET HIM BACK TO THE NANNY.

04:56.166 --> 04:59.125
CAN YOU, UM, TELL GINSBERG
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK?
MM-HMM. YEAH. ALL RIGHT.

04:59.166 --> 05:01.125
(babbles)
SAY BYE-BYE. SAY BYE-BYE.

05:01.166 --> 05:02.583
SEE YOU LATER, BUDDY?

05:02.625 --> 05:05.000
