THIS ISN'T YOUR FAULT?

05:22.375 --> 05:24.041
(inhales deeply)

05:24.083 --> 05:25.375
LOOK. HEY, LOOK AT ME.

05:25.417 --> 05:26.625
(groans)

05:26.667 --> 05:28.834
LOOK AT ME.

05:28.875 --> 05:31.000
THIS IS NOT YOUR FAULT.

05:35.083 --> 05:36.333
IT IS.

05:36.375 --> 05:39.166
BUT THANK YOU
FOR SAYING IT ISN'T.

05:45.083 --> 05:48.041
(elevator bell dings)

05:48.083 --> 05:50.333
OH, CHARLOTTE. GOOD.
I'M GLAD YOU'RE HERE.

05:50.375 --> 05:52.333
I-I CAN'T DO
THE SEX ED SEMINAR

05:52.375 --> 05:55.125
AT THE RETIREMENT HOME
TONIGHT.
YOU ARE NOT BAILING ON ME?

05:55.166 --> 05:57.125
UH, WELL, NOT BY CHOICE.

05:57.166 --> 05:59.333
I HAVE A PATIENT.
