GIVE CRAPPY ADVICE.

06:31.750 --> 06:35.333
NO, ACTUALLY,
I'M KINDA... BRILLIANT.

06:36.834 --> 06:37.917
(laughs)

06:40.959 --> 06:43.041
APPLICATION
FOR THE FDA APPROVAL

06:43.083 --> 06:45.041
