ANY IMPROVEMENT.

07:11.166 --> 07:14.125
DID NAOMI SAY WHEN, UH,
THEY'RE PLANNING ON COMING BACK?
NO.

07:14.166 --> 07:17.125
THEN MOVE THAT
TO THE TOP OF THE PILE

07:17.166 --> 07:19.125
SO THEY HAVE A REASON TO.

07:19.166 --> 07:22.166
(motor whirring)

07:24.083 --> 07:26.041
COME ON, CHARLOTTE.
SEX ED FOR SENIORS?

07:26.083 --> 07:28.667
