09:32.667 --> 09:35.709
THAT JUST BECAUSE THE RISK
OF PREGNANCY IS GONE,

09:35.750 --> 09:38.208
THE RISK OF CONTRACTING SEXUALLY
TRANSMITTED DISEASES ISN'T.

09:38.250 --> 09:40.208
