IN A PLACE OF THIS SIZE,

09:40.250 --> 09:42.583
WHERE MANY OF YOU ARE SO...

09:42.625 --> 09:47.041
(clock ticking)

09:47.083 --> 09:51.041
SO LUCKY TO BE ENJOYING
CONSIDERABLE LEISURE TIME...

09:51.083 --> 09:52.417
UH, E-EXACTLY.

09:52.458 --> 09:53.667
YEAH.

09:53.709 --> 09:55.333
